data.description: Welcome to 211 Wintergreen Road, a classic 2-story residence nestled in the heart of an established and friendly neighborhood. This charming home offers the perfect combination of timeless appeal and modern comfort, providing an inviting space for family living.As you approach the welcoming front porch, you'll envision yourself enjoying quiet evenings and morning coffees.. Step inside to discover a freshly painted interior, radiating with warmth and natural light, creating a welcoming ambiance throughout.The main floor features many things: foyer, mudroom, flex space under the staircase, and a spacious living area that's perfect for relaxing with loved ones or entertaining guests.The highlight of this home is the master bedroom downstairs, offering convenience and privacy for homeowners seeking single level living if needed. The master suite boasts  dual closet space and easy access to the full bathroom. Upstairs, you'll find two guest bedrooms, each with its own vanity area for added convenience and privacy, while sharing a tub/shower. This unique layout provides comfort and privacy for family members or guests. The heart of the home is the cozy eat-in kitchen, equipped with modern appliances, ample cabinet space, and a breakfast bar, where you can gather for delicious meals and lively conversations. Outside, the spacious backyard offers endless possibilities for outdoor enjoyment and recreation, whether it's gardening, playing with pets, or hosting summer barbecues with friends and family on the concrete deck! This location offers an easy commute to surrounding counties and is within minutes from Downtown Walterboro!
